%pyspark

def create_key(row):
    
    sec = int(datetime.strptime(row['DTHR'], '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S').second)
    mi =  str(datetime.strptime(row['DTHR'], '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S').minute)
    hr =  str(datetime.strptime(row['DTHR'], '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S').hour)
    
    partition = ''
    if(sec <= 20):
         partition = hr+'-'+mi+'-020'
    elif(sec > 20 and sec <= 40):
        partition = hr+'-'+mi+'-040'
    else:
        partition = hr+'-'+mi+'-060'
    
    key = row['COD_LINHA']+'-'+str(row['DATA'])+'-'+partition
    return key


def run_dbscan(df):
    
    key    = df[0]
    values = df[1]
    
    d = [{'cod_linha'         :values[i]['COD_LINHA'], \
          'veic'              :values[i]['VEIC'],\
          'dthr'              :values[i]['DTHR'],\
          'discrete_dt_event' :values[i]['DISCRETE_DT_EVENT'], \
          'lat'               :float(values[i]['LAT']),\
          'lon'               :float(values[i]['LON'])} for i in range(0,len(values))]
    
    coordinates = pd.DataFrame(d)
    
    db = DBSCAN(eps=0.5/6371., min_samples=3, algorithm='ball_tree', metric='haversine') \
         .fit_predict(np.radians(coordinates[['lat','lon']]))

    coordinates['cluster_id'] = db
    coordinates['key'] = key 
    return  coordinates.to_dict("records")


def create_discretized_event(col):
    
    
    sec = int(datetime.strptime(col, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S').second)
    discrete_dt_hr = ''
    if(sec <= 20):
        discrete_dt_hr = datetime.strptime(col, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S').replace(second=20)
    elif(sec > 20 and sec <= 40):
        discrete_dt_hr = datetime.strptime(col, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S').replace(second=40)
    else:
        discrete_dt_hr = datetime.strptime(col, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S').replace(second=59)
    
    return str(discrete_dt_hr)
    
    
toDiscretizedEvent =  udf(lambda x: create_discretized_event(x))


toDateTime =  udf(lambda x: datetime.strptime(x, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S'), DateType())

%pyspark
path='/work/datascience/data/urbs/2018-11/19-23/'

position_events = sqlContext.read.json(path+'*_veiculos.json')

position_events = position_events.withColumn("DATA", toDateTime(col('DTHR')))

position_events = position_events.withColumn("DISCRETE_DT_EVENT", toDiscretizedEvent(position_events.DTHR))

%pyspark
clusters_df = position_events.rdd                         \
    .map(lambda x: (create_key(x), x))                    \
    .map(lambda x: (x[0], [x[1]]))                        \
    .reduceByKey(lambda a, b: a + b)                      \
    .map(lambda x: run_dbscan(x))                         \
    .flatMap(lambda x: [item for item in x])              \
    .map(lambda l: Row(**dict(l))).toDF()
